CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 1, 1954, pg. 10, reads: "Recital - Joseph W. Grider, head of the music department at West Virginia State College, was presented in recital last Sunday, April 25, by Marie Carter Hayes in a magnificent concert which ended the musical season in Pittsburgh... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Joseph W. Grider playing piano in Hayes School of Music, 6490 Frankstown Avenue, East Liberty
